</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a snap ring expander, install the snap ring.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="D033851E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000010UU00RX_01_0002" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00001DV00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL INPUT SHAFT BEARING</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C086536E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Coat the 13 input shaft bearings with MP grease, and install them to the input shaft.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM0000010UU00RX_01_0003" proc-id="RM21Q0EV__00001DW00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL NO. 2 SYNCHRONIZER RING</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C067214E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>Coat the No. 2 synchronizer ring with gear oil, and install it to the input shaft.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
